<div class="kt" id="6EC52BB9-DA1E-4992-876EDB4EE7CC4F67">
<h4>Cooperation:</h4>
<div><p>The FIDUCIA consortium contains 13 research institutes led by the University of Parma. The project is co-funded by the EU through the Seventh Framework Programme for Research and Development. Results are presented at annual international conferences and research findings are discussed with European politicians and policy makers. A final report will be published at the end of the project.</p></div>
